Author: TerawattLED
Title: Terawatt Private Sale, PreICO, ICO Coming Soon
Body: Terawatt is a patent-pending, renewable energy blockchain startup, with a strong focus on monetization and driving global L.E.D. adoption. Terawatt will create a Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO), and also create a highly deflationary Ethereum-based currency for global payments. The DAO will be funded and used by Utility Companies, L.E.D. Sellers, Businesses, Token Holders, and Energy Customers worldwide. The DAO will act as a decentralized global mutual/insurance fund to ensure Utilities (and businesses) always have access to funding (which constantly runs out) for subsidizing L.E.D. sales to their energy customers (or for buying L.E.D.s).  Total Supply: 100 Million Tokens Circulating Supply: 65 million (We will use 50-75% of profits from fees to buyback and burn our coins everyday to reduce supply 50% to 32.5 million or less over the next few years*)  Competitors: None Private sale: June 2018 PreICO: July 2018 ICO: September 2018  Telegram Group:  https://t.me/joinchat/F3V8JRIbuwgLQUT4Tp_LMg  Twitter:  https://twitter.com/TeraWatt_2018  Join Mailing List and Read White Paper: http://terawattled.com  ICO Listings  KICKICO: https://www.kickico.com/campaigns/52508/terawatt  ICO Bench: https://icobench.com/ico/terawatt  ICO Examiner: https://www.icoexaminer.com/community/members/terawatt.926/  ICO Bull: https://icosbull.com/eng/ico/terawatt  ICO Marks: https://icomarks.com/ico/terawatt  Bounty: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4566082  Partners  The Tip Token: https://thetiptoken.io/home/ Genesis Token: https://www.genesistoken.net/index.html Carbon Check: http://www.carboncheck.co.in/  Applicature: http://applicature.com
